godhcp (1.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Drop golang-go and dh-systemd build dependencies; build with the Go
    toolchain installed on the host as declared in go.mod
  * Remove obsolete --with=systemd dh sequence (systemd handled by the
    maintainer scripts); pin GOTOOLCHAIN=local to avoid network downloads
  * Bump go directive to 1.26.4
  * Fix DHCP option override correctness (apply overrides to ACK, decode
    hex options) and harden runtime paths against crashes

 -- Fabrice Durand <fdurand@inverse.ca>  Tue, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

godhcp (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add web UI for configuration management
  * Add GET /api/v1/config endpoint to retrieve configuration
  * Add POST /api/v1/config endpoint to update configuration
  * Implement modern, responsive web interface
  * Support for managing interfaces, networks, and DHCP options
  * Add comprehensive form validation and error handling

 -- Fabrice Durand <fdurand@inverse.ca>  Fri, 08 Nov 2025 16:00:00 +0000

godhcp (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Multi-interface DHCP server support
  * DHCP relay functionality
  * Static IP assignments
  * IP pool management with multiple algorithms
  * REST API for monitoring
  * Systemd integration

 -- Fabrice Durand <fdurand@inverse.ca>  Mon, 17 Mar 2020 00:00:00 +0000
